- AJAX Marker Management
 * Write a script to precompute which zoom level each POI should be 
visible at.

- AJAX API
 * Design and implement a caching mechanism to avoid a DB query and XML 
generation every time the map is displayed, moved, or zoomed.
 * Use a standards based XML format (GPX) or define an appropriate 
schema.

- Data Loaders
 * Re-write the Ottawa Public Library loader in PHP.
